casebody.data:
No. 1219,

Misc.

Traub v. Connecticut. Petitioner pro se. John D. LaBelle and Harry W. Hultgren, Jr. for respondent.

Motion to use the record in No. 1285, Mise., October Term, 1962, granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Errors of Connecticut denied.

Mr. Justice Douglas is of the opinion that certiorari should be granted.
